# LeakSanitizer suppressions for statgrab CI ASan job.
#
# This file should normally be empty. Add entries here only for leaks
# inside PHP core or system libraries that surface during shutdown of
# the cli SAPI. Do NOT suppress leaks coming from libstatgrab or from
# the statgrab extension itself: those are exactly what this job is
# meant to catch.
#
# Format: leak:<substring matched against any frame in the stack>
